metadata.description: One day you will wake up, with a heavy load on your shoulders. the problems will not end, the trials will not get easier, and every time you want to quit and see no point in trying. and at that moment only you yourself will lift you up. you from the future, only you WHO always believes in YOU! and knows that you can always overcome any challenge. Look into this future and never stop.
